                     <interp inst="t18280529-5-person117" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was passing, and saw Dr. Holland holding the prisoner; he gave him to me with the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was coming down Fleet-market after delivering a parcel for my father; I picked this handkerchief up - the prosecutor took it from me, and said he had no doubt I had stolen it. <rs id="t18280529-5-verdict23" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18280529-5-verdict23" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY. Aged 17. Recommended to Mercy by Prosecutor, understanding that he had borne a good character. Judgment Respited
